Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.-90,0:00:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people seek\Nthe answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future--\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright, but I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really, really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really need\Neverything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.59,0:01:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.97,0:01:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming!\NShoot it, quickly! Shoot it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.26,0:02:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.00,0:02:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu! Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.04,0:02:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.18,0:02:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Through the Sky They Soar!\NThe 1,000-Year Legend Lives Again!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.79,0:02:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.29,0:02:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to going to the\Ndragons' nest?! Try hard to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.09,0:02:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.96,0:02:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Grandpa Ryu!\N--Damn those guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.70,0:02:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--This is bad!\N--Yeah. He can't swim, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:03:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whew, what a scare...\NIt suddenly came right for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.69,0:03:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commodore! The Millennial\NDragon is starting to sink!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.72,0:03:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fret! We'll still make it in time!\NFire a harpoon and drag it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.25,0:03:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Target the Millennial Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.75,0:03:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.57,0:03:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:04:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've no idea of the value of the\Nthing you're standing on right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I want are the\NMillennial Dragon's bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.38,0:04:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I have its Dragonite,\NI can attain everlasting life!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu isn't a thing!\NHe's our friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.25,0:04:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a dear friend\Nwho's on a journey with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.92,0:04:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What utter nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.03,0:04:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, you can sink\Ninto the sea with your friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.46,0:04:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you try to harpoon me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire at that brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.03,0:04:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But, if we do that, we'll blow\Nthe Millennial Dragon up, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter!\NBone fragments will do just fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.18,0:05:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir! Aim the\Nsub-cannons out to sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're fine staying here?!\NWhat kind of wimpiness is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.42,0:05:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still haven't\Naccomplished your goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to going to your nest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up by saying\Nyou're staying here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.27,0:05:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I will!\NDon't worry about Apis!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.94,0:05:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just think about yourself now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.25,0:05:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Untie these ropes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.58,0:05:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I gotta go to Grandpa Ryu!\N--What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.29,0:05:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta save Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.56,0:05:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Leave Grandpa Ryu to Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.06,0:05:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no!\NI gotta go! I gotta go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:05:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If anyone, he'll manage somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.36,0:06:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The entire sea is shaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.57,0:06:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?! What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.62,0:06:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.62,0:06:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?! What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? So that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.47,0:06:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There shouldn't be any underwater\Nvolcanoes in these waters!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter! Fire! Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.24,0:07:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have dear friends of your own, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.52,0:07:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Grandpa Ryu!\N--What's he bellowing for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.99,0:07:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's calling...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calling?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's telling Millennial Dragons\Nall around the world that it's "time"...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.40,0:07:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's "time"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.57,0:07:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.94,0:07:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! W-What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.06,0:08:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So many Millennial Dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.97,0:08:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--These're Grandpa Ryu's friends!\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.57,0:08:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What the...?!\N--Where the hell'd they come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.21,0:08:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Those are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.18,0:08:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragonite!\NIt's a mother lode of Dragonite!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot them! Shoot them down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We can't! Our cannons\Ncan't reach that high!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.44,0:08:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.94,0:09:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I know!\NI promise I'll tell Apis!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.74,0:09:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.25,0:09:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gonna borrow your neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...And...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.62,0:09:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Battle-Axe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.80,0:09:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.45,0:10:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.46,0:11:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.40,0:11:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The commodore's been beaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.65,0:11:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Troops sure are weak once\Ntheir bosses are taken out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.12,0:11:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they just gonna reel in\Ntheir chains and run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.22,0:11:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We better get goin' too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.93,0:11:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're circling around...\NWhat's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.10,0:11:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.03,0:11:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.34,0:11:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The chains!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.47,0:11:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You idiots! What're you doing?!\N--We're gonna crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.38,0:11:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's really somethin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.51,0:11:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san! I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.15,0:11:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Just get on already!\N--Where's Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.75,0:11:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.22,0:11:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.39,0:12:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to bother you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.77,0:12:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yo!\N--Don't give me, "Yo!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.63,0:12:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you come back more quietly?!\NYou're gonna wreck the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.41,0:12:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.55,0:12:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--An earthquake?\N--Again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.78,0:12:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.62,0:12:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't able to keep my\Npromise to you, Grandpa Ryu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.42,0:12:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't able to take\Nyou to the dragons' nest...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.19,0:12:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Grandpa Ryu's wish came true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.10,0:12:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you hear the\NMillennial Dragons' voices?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.65,0:13:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.02,0:13:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with these earthquakes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.26,0:13:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This one's big!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.53,0:13:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-The sea's pulling way back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what it meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.99,0:13:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Nami-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.26,0:13:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dragons' nest really is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.99,0:13:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not called "Millennial Dragons"\Nbecause of their life spans!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.16,0:13:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because they come to this\Nisland only once every 1,000 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.04,0:13:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Millennial Dragons are migratory!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.41,0:14:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's by no coincidence that\Nthey've all flocked here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.05,0:14:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no wonder they call it Lost Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.58,0:14:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it only surfaces\Nonce every 1,000 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.72,0:14:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So of course no one today\Nremembers the last time it surfaced!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.76,0:14:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now... this very moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is when the dragons' nest has appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.23,0:14:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.73,0:15:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, is that what I think it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.96,0:15:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It must be the dragon nest\NGrandpa Ryu wanted to go back to!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.50,0:15:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.01,0:15:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--H-Hey! Apis!\N--Apis!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.35,0:15:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Why'd she suddenly run off?\N--Grandpa Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.25,0:15:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu is here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu! Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.94,0:16:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just by coincidence,\Nthe place Grandpa Ryu sunk
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.71,0:16:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was where the dragons' nest was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you suppose that might\Nhelp him rest in peace better?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.72,0:16:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay! He said his wish\Ncame true when he was sinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.33,0:16:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the dragons' nest?\NLook at all these weird rocks...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.63,0:16:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think they're probably\Nmade of Dragonite...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.17,0:16:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.17,0:16:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this rock here.\NDoesn't it look just like a dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, now that you mention it...\NBut why are the rocks dragons?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.17,0:16:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because they were on the ocean floor\Nfor a thousand long years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.81,0:16:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The materials in their bodies fossilized.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.48,0:16:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.78,0:16:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Do you really get it?\N--Nope! Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.55,0:16:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say when elephants are about to die,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:17:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they hide themselves\Nin their elephant graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.89,0:17:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the same is true here.\NThis might be a dragon graveyard...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.73,0:17:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dragon graveyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.27,0:17:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! It's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.97,0:17:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu said going back\Nto his nest would make him better!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.47,0:17:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be a graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.64,0:17:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apis...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.91,0:17:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu was\Na lost Millennial Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.48,0:17:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was all alone,\Nfor a thousand years...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.72,0:17:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he made friends with you, Apis.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.79,0:17:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said out of the\N1,000 years he was alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.26,0:17:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this last year with\Nyou was his happiest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy... You understand\Nthe dragons' language?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.14,0:17:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just somehow know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.48,0:17:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, talk about half-baked...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.38,0:17:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.11,0:17:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You liar...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.85,0:17:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a liar, Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.88,0:18:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is the dragons' nest...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.92,0:18:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you've made it back to the dragons' nest,\Nthen open your eyes again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.06,0:18:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get better!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.37,0:18:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu wasn't lying at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.14,0:18:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said that Millennial Dragons\Nreturn to the nest every 1,000 years
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.28,0:18:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and are reborn again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.98,0:18:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.75,0:18:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A baby Millennial Dragon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.17,0:19:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.07,0:19:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.99,0:19:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Apis.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.96,0:19:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't just a\NMillennial Dragon graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.60,0:20:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's a place\Nthat connects to new life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.44,0:20:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Thank you, everyone!\N--Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.01,0:20:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For bringing Grandpa Ryu\Nback to the dragons' nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.78,0:20:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I realize it now, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I realize what kind of place this is,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.78,0:20:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and why Grandpa Ryu\Nwanted to return here so badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.12,0:20:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apis...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.55,0:20:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an amazing place, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.79,0:20:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I understand why my ancestors\Nwent so far as to build a temple...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.90,0:20:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.47,0:20:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's go back to the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.30,0:20:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone there must be worried,\Nand probably surprised, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.91,0:20:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.24,0:20:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's hurry back to\Nthe ship and leave the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.98,0:20:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whew, I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.22,0:20:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji! Make me some food!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.32,0:20:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah!\N--Meat! Make meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.39,0:20:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have sautéed veggies\Nwith lots of bean sprouts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.59,0:20:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where've I heard that before?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.53,0:21:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, these rocks are cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.00,0:21:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These all used to be\NMillennial Dragons?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.94,0:21:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it looks that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.40,0:21:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they are Dragonite,\Nthere's no way to extract it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.24,0:21:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the whole elixir\Nof immortality thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.74,0:21:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was nothing but a\Ndream within a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.88,0:21:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we took these\Ncoral-covered fossils back with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.45,0:21:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'd never get an elixir from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.45,0:21:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.85,0:21:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning those Navy bastards\Ndid all that work for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.37,0:21:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fools! As if I would ever\Nkick the bucket so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.40,0:21:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must pay you back\Nfor what you've done!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.07,0:21:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But first...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.58,0:21:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Millennial Dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.85,0:21:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this many, I can have\Nall the Dragonite I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.72,0:22:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.36,0:22:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eric! Look!\NA flock of Millennial Dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.76,0:22:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay you money!\NWhat do you say to another deal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.07,0:22:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can make elixirs of immortality\Nfrom living Millennial Drag--!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.27,0:22:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.07,0:22:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My overflowing feelings don't connect
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.07,0:22:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as I firmly squeeze your hand back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.98,0:22:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll set off by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.91,0:23:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so keep watching me intently\Nas I go into the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.76,0:23:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about it\Na bit since this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.76,0:23:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it so hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.33,0:23:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting from some point, I haven't\Nbeen able to get away from that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.81,0:23:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to catch those\Nfeelings that rushed off,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.68,0:23:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm already about\Nto overtake myself, even
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to embrace my\Ndreams that have jumped out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.56,0:23:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With you, I can run there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.07,0:23:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's Eric!\N--Man, he's stubborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.41,0:24:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'll handle him.\N--No, I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.71,0:24:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.81,0:24:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lost Island, huh?\NIt's sad to leave it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.28,0:24:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Set sail! The Grand Line,\Nat last! Isn't this great?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.89,0:24:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.42,0:24:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--There it is!\N--So that's the Red Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.52,0:24:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.79,0:24:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"An Angry Showdown!\NCross the Red Line!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.73,0:24:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
